<139>Usage:
	<029>scan [add|del|purge|list] [<pattern>]

scan_aid highlights output of the scan command based on basic pattern matching.

	scan add <pattern> - adds the pattern to the highlight list
	scan del <pattern> - removed the pattern from the highlight list
	scan purge - clears the highlight list
	scan list - lists all patterns that are to be highlighted

You can change the color by setting the _mod_scan_aid_setting[color] variable.

